                "Pd-109 - 2.80.",
                "Enriched samples of Pd-108 (99.5%) and Pd-106 (95.96%)",
                "of weights 52.7 mg and 34.7 mg, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "TOF spectrum owing to the Pd-105(n,gamma) reaction was",
                "carefully extracted by gating on 512-keV ground-state",
                "transition gamma-ray in the pulse-height spectrum of",
                "Pd-107.",
                "Relative neutron capture cross sections of Pd-105",
                "were derived from the neutron flux and the net TOF",
                "spectrum. Relative cross sections were normalized to",
                "the value of JENDL-3.3 at 1 eV."
              ]
            }
          ],
